%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Parasite'%20director%20Bong%20Joon-ho%20demands%20police%20investigate%20the%20death%20of%20Lee%20Sun-kyun%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221194%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bong%20Joon-ho%20and%20Lee%20Sun-kyun%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a240c243bb77284b9cf748%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22896%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBong%20Joon-ho%20and%20Lee%20Sun-kyun%3Cp%3EMichael%20Kovac%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20AFI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBong%20Joon-ho%20wants%20police%20to%20investigate%20the%20death%20of%C2%A0Lee%20Sun-kyun.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELee%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20a%20park%20after%20undergoing%20a%20long%20interrogation%20by%20police.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPrior%20to%20his%20death%2C%20Lee%20had%20been%20under%20investigation%20for%20drug%20use.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOscar-winning%20%26quot%3BParasite%26quot%3B%20director%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparasite-director-bong-joon-ho-says-would-never-direct-marvel-movie-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBong%20Joon-ho%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20artists%20in%20South%20Korea%20have%20called%20for%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20the%20death%20of%20popular%20actor%20Lee%20Sun-kyun%2C%20who%20played%20the%20head%20of%20a%20wealthy%20family%20in%20the%20class%20satire%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELee%2C%2048%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flee-sun-kyun-found-dead-reports-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efound%20dead%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20car%20on%20December%2027%20in%20what%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20a%20suicide%20following%20an%20intense%20weekslong%20police%20investigation%20into%20his%20alleged%20drug%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%2C%20found%20in%20a%20park%20in%20Seoul%20after%20being%20reported%20missing%20by%20his%20manager%2C%20had%20left%20a%20note%20that%20his%20wife%20later%20discovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBong%2C%20along%20with%20other%20artists%20part%20of%20the%20Association%20of%20Solidarity%20Among%20Cultural%20Artists%2C%20released%20a%20planned%20statement%20in%20a%20nationally%20televised%20press%20conference%20in%20Seoul%2C%20criticizing%20how%20police%20handled%20Lee's%20drug%20investigation%20as%20well%20as%20how%20media%20reported%20aspects%20of%20Lee's%20personal%20life.%20They%20also%20asked%20that%20officials%20%26quot%3Brevise%20the%20law%20to%20protect%20the%20human%20rights%20of%20artists.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20urge%20relevant%20officials%20to%20fully%20investigate%20whether%20there%20were%20any%20problems%20with%20the%20security%20of%20(the%20information)%20in%20the%20police%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20Lee%20had%20suffered%20%26quot%3Bsevere%20character%20assassination%26quot%3B%20before%20his%20death%20and%20called%20for%20revisions%20of%20laws%20to%20protect%20human%20rights%20in%20criminal%20investigations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20had%20been%20investigating%20allegations%20that%20Lee%20used%20illegal%20drugs%20at%20the%20residence%20of%20a%20bar%20hostess.%20Lee%20insisted%20he%20was%20tricked%20into%20taking%20the%20drugs%20and%20that%20he%20did%20not%20know%20what%20they%20were%2C%20according%20to%20South%20Korean%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20prompted%20extensive%20tabloid%20coverage%20of%20Lee%20and%20unconfirmed%20online%20rumors%20about%20his%20private%20life.%20Lee%20filed%20a%20suit%20against%20two%20people%2C%20including%20the%20hostess%2C%20alleging%20they%20blackmailed%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELee%20had%20been%20subjected%20to%20multiple%20interrogations%20by%20police%20over%20the%20claims%20of%20drug%20use.%20During%20the%20week%20of%20his%20death%2C%20Lee%20had%20completed%20an%20interrogation%20that%20lasted%2019%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20the%20police%20make%20a%20good%20judgment%20about%20whose%20side's%20statements%20are%20credible%20between%20me%20and%20the%20blackmailers%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20told%20reporters%20following%20the%20lengthy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flee-sun-kyun-actor-parasite-dead-suicide-drug-use-investigation-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Einterrogation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparasite-movie-review-plot-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%26quot%3BParasite%26quot%3B%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20won%20Oscars%20for%20best%20picture%20and%20three%20other%20categories%20in%202020.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20non-English-language%20film%20to%20win%20Best%20Picture%20in%20the%20Academy%20Awards%20history%20and%20the%20first%20South%20Korean%20movie%20to%20win%20an%20Oscar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELee%2C%20who%20played%20Park%20Dong-ik%20in%20the%20film%2C%20won%20a%20Screen%20Actors%20Guild%20award%20for%20his%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korea%20has%20strict%20anti-drug%20laws%20and%20has%20long%20had%20the%20highest%20suicide%20rate%20among%20developed%20countries.%20It%20has%20experienced%20a%20string%20of%20celebrity%20suicides%20involving%20K-pop%20stars%2C%20prominent%20politicians%2C%20and%20business%20executives.%20Many%20of%20the%20celebrity%20suicides%20have%20been%20blamed%20on%20malicious%20and%20abusive%20online%20comments%20and%20severe%20cyberbullying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20has%20also%20been%20cracking%20down%20on%20drug%20crimes%20among%20high-profile%20celebrities.%20For%20Koreans%2C%20drug%20use%20%E2%80%94%20even%20abroad%20%E2%80%94%20can%20result%20in%20prison%20for%20six%20months.%20Repeat%20offenders%20or%20dealers%20can%20face%20up%20to%2014%20years%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKorean%20celebrities%20that%20have%20faced%20drug%20scandals%20include%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.yna.co.kr%2Fview%2FAEN201707200