%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fadult-film-star-thaina-fields-dies-at-24-months-after-she-spoke-about-abuse-in-porn-industry-4847313%5C%22%3EThaina%20Fields%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20a%20well-known%20adult%20film%20star%20in%20Peru.%20Known%20as%20%E2%80%9CChinita%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20became%20a%20prominent%20figure%20in%20the%20adult%20film%20industry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMs%20Fields%20stepped%20into%20the%20Peruvian%20entertainment%20scene%20through%20her%20participation%20in%20the%20clown%20programme%20Chupetin%20Trujillo.%20She%20then%20collaborated%20with%20the%20production%20company%20Mily%20Peru%2C%20known%20for%20creating%20adult%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Fields%20spoke%20about%20her%20struggle%20with%20anxiety%20and%20seeking%20psychological%20help.%20%26quot%3BWe%20all%20have%20traumas.%20I%20suffer%20from%20dysthymia%20and%20obsessive-compulsive%20disorder%2C%20I%20have%20psychosis%2C%20and%20I%20take%20pills%20for%20that%2C%20to%20sleep.%20Therapy%20and%20medication%20is%20what%20has%20helped%20me%20be%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShe%20also%20spoke%20about%20going%20through%20sexual%20harassment%20within%20the%20industry%20eight%20months%20before%20her%20untimely%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20were%20her%20accusations%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Fields%20revealed%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20strong.%20Initially%2C%20I%20decided%20not%20to%20sue.%20I%20have%20suffered%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20abuse%20after%20starting%20to%20create%20adult%20content.%20At%20first%20many%20thought%20that%20by%20hiring%20me%20they%20could%20do%20what%20they%20wanted%20with%20me%2C%20but%20then%20I%20came%20home%2C%20took%20a%20bath%2C%20and%20cried.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20told%