%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a226ee6979d73718232606%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDolls%20seized%20by%20authorities%20are%20displayed%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20to%20explain%20what%20they%20are%20made%20of%20at%20the%20Archeology%20Museum%20in%20Lima%2C%20Peru.%3Cp%3EMartin%20Mejia%20via%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20of%20Peru%20has%20long%20inspired%20speculation%20about%20alien%20visits%20to%20Earth%2C%20with%20its%20famous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-researchers-discover-more-mysterious-biomorphs-in-peru-nazca-lines-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENazca%20lines%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20iconic%20temples%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplaces-people-think-aliens-built-2018-7%23machu-picchu-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMacchu%20Picchu%3C%2Fa%3E%20drawing%20the%20attention%20of%20skeptics%20who%20argue%20extraterrestrials%20are%20the%20only%20explanation%20for%20such%20tremendous%20feats%20of%20engineering%20and%20ancient%20architectural%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20lack%20of%20scientific%20evidence%20to%20support%20those%20theories%20doesn't%20stop%20them%20from%20trying%20to%20pass%20off%20mysterious%20discoveries%20as%20proof%20of%20otherworldly%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMexican%20journalist%20Jos%C3%A9%20Jaime%20Maussan%20and%20some%20Mexican%20lawmakers%20became%20the%20subject%20of%20international%20ridicule%20in%20September%20when%20he%20went%20before%20the%20country's%20congress%20to%20present%20two%20boxes%20with%20supposed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faliens-mexico-congress-species-jose-maussan-peru-extraterrestrials-fake-mummies-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emummies%20found%20in%20Peru%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20others%20claimed%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bnon-human%20beings%20t