https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fmovies%2Fcelebrities%2Fstory%2Fexclusive-ira-khan-nupur-shikhare-wedding-reception-2500-guests-celebrities-9-cuisines-2488023-2024-01-12%5C%22%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%2C%20over%202500%20guests%20are%20expected%20to%20attend%20the%20function%20at%20the%20Bandra%20Kurla%20Complex%20(BKC)%20venue.%20Nine%20different%20kinds%20of%20cuisines%20will%20be%20served%20for%20the%20guests%20and%20Gujarati%20menu%20will%20dominate%20the%20chart%2C%20according%20to%20that%20report.%20India%20Today%20quoted%20a%20source%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BAamir%20Khan%20has%20extended%20a%20warm%20invitation%20to%20everyone%20in%20the%20industry.%20From%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20to%20Salman%20Khan%2C%20Ambanis%2C%20Kapoors%2C%20Bhatts%2C%20Deols%2C%20everyone%20is%20expected%20to%20attend%20the%20grand%20wedding%20reception%20in%20Mumbai.%20For%20the%20wedding%20reception%2C%20Ambanis%20have%20given%20their%20venue%20at%20NMACC%20to%20accommodate%20the%20guests.%26quot%3B%20The%20source%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Khans%20have%20kept%20a%20plethora%20of%20menus%20for%20guests.%20A%20total%20of%209%20different%20state%20cuisines%20are%20a%20part%20of%20the%20reception%20menu.%20The%20Gujarati%20menu%20apparently%20dominates%20the%20palate%2C%20with%20Lucknowi%20and%20Maharashtrian%20food%20also%20on%20the%20list.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fira-khan-and-nupur-shikhare-with-aamir-khan-kiran-rao-reena-dutta-junaid-and-azad-in-a-grand-pic-from-their-wedding-4843290%5C%22%3EIra%20Khan%20and%20Nupur%20Shikhare%3C%2Fa%3E%20exchanged%20rings%20and%20vows%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20family%20and%20friends%20in%20Udaipur%20on%20January%2010.%20The%20white%20wedding%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20three-day%20celebrations%20comprising%20mehendi%2C%20sangeet%2C%20dinner%20night%20and%20a%20pyjama%20party.%20The%20photos%20from%20the%20vows%20ceremony%20were%20shared%20by%20the%20official%20wedding