ve%20with%20the%20Purple%20Mattress%20Protector%20was%20the%20strong%20initial%20odor%20it%20had%20out%20of%20the%20box.%20Fortunately%2C%20it%20dissipated%20by%20bedtime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20budget%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221165%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Saferest%20premium%20mattress%20protector%20on%20a%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63c991d3eee94d001a78fdc1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22874%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20budget-friendly%20SafeRest%20Premium%20Mattress%20Protector%20fits%20mattresses%20up%20to%2018%20inches%20thick.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tested%20four%20mattress%20protectors%20that%20cost%20less%20than%20%2430.%20Of%20those%2C%20the%20SafeRest%20Premium%20Mattress%20Protector%20performed%20the%20best.%20In%20addition%20to%20remaining%20leak-free%20in%20our%20tests%2C%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20at%20staying%20cool%20and%20dissipating%20heat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SafeRest%20protector%20can%20fit%20a%20broad%20range%20of%20mattresses%20up%20to%2018%20inches%20thick.%20As%20with%20many%20protectors%2C%20the%20part%20that%20rests%20on%20top%20of%20your%20mattress%20is%20made%20of%20a%20different%20material%20than%20the%20skirt%20around%20the%20sides.%20The%20top%20is%20waterproof%2C%20while%20the%20sides%20are%20not.%20Fortunately%2C%20the%20top%20fit%20my%20mattress%20well%20and%20covered%20it%20to%20the%20edges%2C%20even%20after%20putting%20it%20through%20the%20washer%20and%20dryer%20five%20times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20surface%20is%20terry%20cloth%20and%20not%20the%20most%20comfortable.%20As%20I%20moved%20in%20the%20night%2C%20it%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20crackling%20noises%2C%20and%20my%20fitted%20sheet%20didn't%20shift%20smoothly%20on%20it.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20a%20solid%20budget%20option%20that%20didn't%20ruin%20my%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20cooling%3Cfigure%