20or%20medium%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EMachine%20wash%2C%20tumble%20dry%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EMachine%20wash%20hot%2C%20tumble%20dry%20low%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EMachine%20wash%20cold%2C%20tumble%20dry%20low%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3Ch3%3EHere%20are%20the%20main%20attributes%20we%20look%20for%20and%20how%20we%20test%20them%3A%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20slept%20on%20each%20mattress%20protector%20(with%20a%20fitted%20sheet%20in%20place)%20and%20rated%20how%20comfortable%20they%20felt%20on%20a%20scale%20of%201%20to%205.%20Most%20protectors%20were%20barely%20noticeable%2C%20and%20none%20scored%20below%20a%203.%20I%20also%20used%20a%20laser%20thermometer%20to%20compare%20the%20temperatures%20before%20lying%20on%20the%20protector%2C%20after%20lying%20on%20it%20for%20at%20least%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20two%20minutes%20after%20getting%20up.%20This%20told%20me%20how%20well%20the%20protector%20dissipated%20heat.%20To%20control%20the%20variables%20that%20might%20affect%20comfort%2C%20I%20used%20the%20same%20mattress%20and%20sheets%20to%20test%20each%20model.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtection%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20placed%20a%20sheet%20of%20paper%20towel%20in%20a%20plastic%20tray%20and%20set%20it%20beneath%20the%20center%20of%20each%20mattress%20protector.%20Next%2C%20I%20poured%20eight%20ounces%20of%20blue%20water%20on%20each%20protector.%20Then%2C%20I%20placed%20a%202-pound%20weight%20on%20the%20liquid%20to%20simulate%20someone%20lying%20on%20it.%20I%20let%20the%20water%20sit%20for%20two%20hours%20before%20checking%20to%20see%20if%20it%20leaked%20through.%20Then%2C%20I%20washed%20and%20dried%20each%20protector%20five%20times%20and%20performed%20the%20test%20again.%20Though%20I%20couldn't%20test%20for%20them%2C%20I%20also%20noted%20if%20the%20protectors%20are%20designed%20to%20protect%20against%20dust%20mites%20and%20bed%20bugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFit%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20put%20each%20protector%20on%20a%20variety%20of%20mattresses%20ranging%20in%20thickness%20from%2010%20inches%20to%2014%20inches%20and%20noted%20how%20difficult%20it%20was%20to%20put%20it%20on%2C%20if%20the%20protector%20bunched%20up%2C%20if%20the%20protective%20top%20covered%20the%20whole%20mattress%20top%2C%20and%20whether%20it%20stayed%20put%20or%20crept%20up%20the%20corners%20throughout%20the%20night.%20Next%2C%20I%20washed%20and%20dried%20the%20protector%20five%20times%20and%20repeated%20the%20test.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENoise%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20polyurethane%20used%20as%20waterproofing%20for%20most%20mattress%20protectors%20sometimes%20makes%20a%20crackling%20sound%20as%20you%20move%20at%20night.%20This%20sound%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20lead%20to%20restless%20sleep%2C%20so%20I%20compared%20all%20of%20the%20protectors%20head-to-head%20to%20see%20how%20loud%20they%20are.%20I%20crinkled%20each%20one%20in%20my%20hands.%20I%20put%20the%20protectors%20in%20order%20from%20quietest%20to%20most%20audible%20as%20I%20did%20this.%20I%20kept%20doing%20this%20until%20I%20was%20confident%20my%20order%20was%20accurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrial%20and%20Warranty%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20most%20foolproof%20way%20to%20know%20if%20a%20mattress%20protector%20is%20comfortable%20for%20you%20is%20to%20sleep%20on%20it%20for%20an%20extended%20period%2C%20so%20a%20lengthy%20trial%20is%20a%20must.%20I%20looked%20at%20the%20length%20of%20the%20trial%20period%20(30%20nights%20was%20the%20median%20of%20the%20protectors%20I%20tested)%20and%20whether%20there%20are%20hidden%20return%20fees.%20I%20also%20looked%20at%20the%20warranty%20length%20(5%20years%20was%20the%20median%20of%20the%20models%20I%20tried).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMattress%20protector%20FAQs%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20mattress%20protector%20displayed%20on%20a%20bed%20in%20the%20corner%20of%20a%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F608b2ca134af8d001859a083%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20mattress%20is%20an%20expensive%20purchase%2C%20so%20it's%20important%20you%20protect%20it%20with%20a%20mattress%20protector%20or%20encasement.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EWhy%20do%20you%20need%20a%20mattress%20protector%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rebecca-robbins.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERebecca%20Robbins%2C%20PhD%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20associate%20scientist%20at%20Brigham%20and%20Women's%20Hospital%20and%20instructor%20in%20medicine%20at%20Harvard%20Medical%20School%2C%20stresses%20the%20importance%20of%20using%20a%20mattress%20protector%20to%20keep%20your%20bed%20free%20of%20dust%20mites%20and%20spills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20to%20protecting%20your%20mattress%20from%20dust%20mites%20and%20other%20allergens%20is%20choosing%20an%20impermeable%20material%2C%20such%20as%20polyurethane%2C%20which%20is%20found%20in%20our%20guide's%20waterproof%20protectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20mattress%20protector%20can%20also%20help%20extend%20the%20general%20life%20of%20your%20mattress%20and%20reduce%20the%20overall%20wear%20and%20tear%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Robbins.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20always%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20when%20you're%20buying%20a%20new%20mattress%2C%20you're%20coupling%20it%20with%20a%20mattress%20protector.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20often%20should%20you%20wash%20a%20mattress%20protector%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20suffer%20from%20allergies%20and%20want%20to%20keep%20dust%20mite%20buildup%20to%20a%20minimum%2C%20we%20recommend%20washing%20your%20protector%20every%20two%20to%20four%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20primary%20concern%20is%20protecting%20your%20mattress%20from%20spills%2C%20we%20recommend%20washing%20it%20once%20every%20two%20to%20six%20months.%20The%20less%20you%20wash%20it%2C%20the%20longer%20the%20waterproof%20polyurethane%20coating%20will%20last.%20However%2C%20clean%20it%20immediately%20if%20you%20have%20an%20accident.%20If%20you're%20using%20a%20mattress%20encasement%20to%20keep%20bed%20bugs%20in%2C%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20remove%20it%20for%20at%20least%2012%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20difference%20between%20a%20mattress%20protector%20and%20encasement%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMattress%20protectors%20usually%20just%20protect%20the%20top%20and%20sides%20of%20your%20mattress%2C%20not%20the%20bottom.%20This%20is%20usually%20enough%20to%20protect%20against%20spills%20and%20dust%20mites.%20Mattress%20encasements%20completely%20engulf%20your%20mattress%2C%20which%20you%20need%20to%20protect%20against%20bed%20bugs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20you%20put%20on%20a%20mattress%20encasement%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EStand%20your%20mattress%20on%20the%20end%2C%20fit%20the%20unzipped%20mattress%20encasement%20over%20the%20top%20of%20the%20mattress%2C%20and%20shimmy%20it%20down.%20Once%20it's%20down%20and%20covering%20the%20mattress%2C%20put%20the%20mattress%20back%20on%20your%20foundation%20and%20zip%20the%20encasement%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3ECan%20mattress%20protectors%20prevent%20bed%20bugs%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20mattress%20protector%20can%20prevent%20bed%20bugs.%20However%2C%20an%20encasement%20can%20keep%20bed%20bugs%20from%20getting%20to%20your%20mattress.%20Encasements%20can%20also%20trap%20bed%20bugs%20already%20in%20your%20mattress%2C%20causing%20them%20to%20starve%20and%20eventually%20die.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheck%20out%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-to-get-rid-of-bed-bugs%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20bed%20bugs%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20tips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20mattress%20protectors%20add%20cushioning%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20mattress%20protectors%20do%20not%20add%20cushioning.%20Instead%2C%20they%20serve%20one%20purpose%3A%20protecting%20your%20bed.%20If%20you're%20looking%20for%20cushioning%2C%20we%20recommend%20adding%20a%20mattress%20topper%20or%20pad%20to%20your%20bed.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-mattress-topper%5C%22%3ECheck%20out%20our%20mattress%20toppers%20guide%20for%20the%20best%20options%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20you%20wash%20a%20mattress%20protector%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20mattress%20protectors%20are%20machine%20washable%20using%20cold%20water.%20Then%20tumble%20dry%20on%20low.%20Most%20protectors%20have%20a%20tag%20attached%20with%20cleaning%20instructions.%20Try%20not%20to%20wash%20it%20too%20often%20since%20it%20tends%20to%20lose%20its%20waterproof%20coating%20the%20more%20you%20wash%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-mattress-protector%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705094021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63c990ae2a1e600018b8c0e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-mattress-protector%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20mattress%20protectors%20are%20non-negotiable%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20protecting%20your%20bed.%20We%20tested%20for%20waterproofing%2C%20breathability%2C%20comfort%2C%20and%20fit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jbrains%40businessinsider.com%20(James%20Brains)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-mattress-protector%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%207%20best%20memory%20foam%20mattresses%20of%202024%2C%20tested%20and%20reviewed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessi