3C%2Fstrong%3E100%20nights%3B%2010%20years%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EShipping%20and%20returns%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFree%20shipping%20and%20returns%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhite-glove%20delivery%20and%20mattress%20removal%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2440%20for%20white-glove%20delivery%2C%20%24125%20for%20all%20non-California%20mattress%20removals%2C%20%240%20for%20California-based%20removals%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDecent%20motion%20isolation%2C%20impressive%20bounce%2C%20soft%20insert%20transforms%20bed%20from%20ultra-firm%20to%20just%20firm%2C%20machine-washable%20cover%2C%20excellent%20edge%20support%2C%20very%20good%20heat%20dissipation%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESide%20sleepers%20will%20find%20this%20uncomfortable%2C%20difficult%20to%20move%20around%2C%20assembly%20required%2C%20expensive%20%244%2C500%20price%20tag%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Airweave%20Mattress%20doesn't%20use%20traditional%20memory%20foam.%20Instead%2C%20it's%20a%20modular%20system%20of%20ultra-firm%20polyethylene%20foam%20with%20an%20open%20structure%20that%20allows%20for%20airflow%2C%20providing%20outstanding%20cooling%20in%20our%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20predominantly%20side%20sleeper%2C%20I%20don't%20like%20firm%20mattresses%2C%20but%20I%20found%20the%20Airweave%20surprisingly%20tolerable%2C%20especially%20when%20I%20added%20the%20removable%20soft%20insert.%20It's%20only%208%20inches%20thick%2C%20thinner%20than%20the%2010%20inches%20I've%20found%20is%20generally%20needed%20for%20a%20supportive%20mattress.%20However%2C%20I%20didn't%20find%20the%20Airweave%20lacking%20in%20support.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bed%20performed%20well%20in%20motion%20isolation%20tests%2C%20and%20the%20edge%20support%20is%20outstanding.%20The%20polyethylene%20was%20quite%20bouncy%2C%20which%20couples%20tend%20to%20like%20during%20sex.%20Whereas%20you%20just%20unbox%20and%20unwrap%20most%20mattresses%2C%20the%20Airweave%20requires%20assembly.%20The%20three%20core%20blocks%20are%20tough%20to%20move%20around%20as%20you%20set%20it%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20the%20best%20memory%20foam%20mattress%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bowling%20ball%20rests%20on%20a%20plain%20white%20mattress%20for%20motion%20transfer%20testing.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F621ce4e1bea1240018a8eaf9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20long%20home%20trial%20is%20an%20important%20consideration%20when%20choosing%20a%20foam%20mattress.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20mattress%20may%20be%20ideal%20for%2099%25%20of%20sleepers%20but%20awful%20for%20you.%20That's%20why%20one%20of%20your%20top%20considerations%20should%20be%20a%20long%20home%20trial.%20This%20allows%20you%20to%20try%20the%20mattress%20at%20home%20for%20several%20nights%20without%20committing%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwmed.edu%2Fnode%2F1599%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMark%20Goetting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20MD%2C%20a%20board-certified%20sleep%20medicine%20specialist%20at%20Western%20Michigan%20University%20Homer%20Stryker%20M.D.%20School%20of%20Medicine%2C%20suggests%20lying%20on%20the%20mattress%20as%20long%20as%20you%20can%20in%20a%20showroom%20before%20buying%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20know%20where%20to%20start%20shopping%20for%20a%20bed%20or%20feel%20uncomfortable%20in%20a%20showroom%2C%20here%20are%20a%20few%20tips%20for%20choosing%20a%20mattress%20based%20on%20how%20you%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESide%20sleepers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Most%20people%20sleep%20on%20their%20side%2C%20and%20fortunately%2C%20%26quot%3Bside%20sleepers%20find%20memory%20foam%20to%20be%20great%20because%20of%20the%20way%20it%20contours%20to%20the%20spine%20and%20creates%20neutral%20alignment%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Derek%20Hales%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20mattress%20review%20site%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnaplab.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENapLab%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20softer-than-average%20mattress%20will%20let%20side%20sleepers%20sink%20in%2C%20helping%20them%20achieve%20spinal%20alignment.%20Zoned%20support%20is%20also%20helpful%20for%20side%20sleepers%20who%20need%20increased%20pressure-point%20relief%20to%20keep%20their%20spine%20aligned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBack%20sleepers%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBack%20sleepers%20don't%20want%20to%20sink%20in%20as%20much%20as%20side%20sleepers%2C%20so%20a%20medium-firm%20mattress%20is%20better.%20When%20you're%20lying%20flat%2C%20it%20will%20keep%20your%20back%20closer%20to%20neutral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStomach%20sleepers%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGoetting%20said%20a%20firm%20mattress%20is%20important%20because%20stomach%20sleepers%20must%20rotate%20their%20head%20to%20breathe%2C%20leaving%20the%20spine%20out%20of%20alignment.%20When%20you%20couple%20this%20with%20a%20pillow%20that%20causes%20your%20head%20to%20flex%20backward%2C%20you're%20more%20prone%20to%20restless%20sleep%20and%20neck%20pain.%20A%20firm%20mattress%20reduces%20the%20degree%20to%20which%20your%20head%20flexes%20backward.%20In%20general%2C%20the%20experts%20I've%20talked%20to%20recommend%20avoiding%20sleeping%20on%20your%20stomach%20if%20you%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20memory%20foam%20mattresses%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20laser%20thermometer%20pointed%20at%20the%20surface%20of%20a%20mattress%20reading%2073%20degrees%20during%20testing.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6216a516081b260018409b0f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20use%20a%20laser%20thermometer%20to%20test%20heat%20dissipation%20for%20each%20mattress.%3Cp%3EJames%20B