jan_at_%25E2%2580%2598Shree_Ram_Janmabhoomi_Mandir%25E2%2580%2599_in_Ayodhya_Uttar_Pradesh_on_August_05_2020.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPredictably%2C%20the%20Sangh%2C%20now%20busy%20at%20the%20temple%20site%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20has%20begun%20lambasting%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20for%20its%20refusal%20to%20attend%20the%20so-called%20consecration%20ceremony.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20grave%20irony%20that%20attends%20this%20political%20configuration%20is%20that%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20has%20made%20precisely%20the%20same%20critique%20of%20the%20forthcoming%20ceremony%20as%20has%20been%20made%20by%20the%20venerated%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Puri%20and%20the%20other%20three%20shankaracharyas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20highly%20regarded%20seer%20has%20remarked%20that%20any%20consecration%20ceremony%20must%20follow%20due%20theological%20processes%2F%20rituals%2C%20as%20laid%20out%2C%20for%20example%2C%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESkand%20Purana.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFailing%20such%20due%20observances%20authorised%20and%20executed%20by%20enshrined%20religious%20heads%2C%20the%20seer%20has%20cautioned%20that%20the%20idol%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20taken%20over%20by%20undesirable%20forces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%2C%20mocking%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20gestures%20that%20habitually%20accompany%20his%20victory%20public%20addresses%2C%20asked%20whether%20he%20(the%20seer)%20is%20expected%20to%20sit%20and%20clap%20while%20Modi%20fronts%20the%20consecration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20seer%20has%20underscored%20the%20unflattering%20point%20that%20the%20event%20is%20merely%20a%20public%20relations%20show%20aimed%20at%20lifting%20the%20electoral%20prospects%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20the%20question%20must%20be%20asked%3A%20who%20is%20more%20proximate%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESanata%20Dharma%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20seer%20of%20Puri%20or%20the%20executive%20head%20of%20the%20constitutional%20republic%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fsanatan-hindu-dharma-highest-guru-ram-temple%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Why%204%20Highest%20Gurus%20of%20Sanatan%20Hindu%20Dharma%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Participate%20in%20Ram%20Temple%20Pranpratistha%2C%E2%80%99%20Explains%20Pro-Hindutva%20Portal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%2C%20if%20the%20Congress%20is%20to%20be%20held%20in%20the%20wrong%20for%20not%20attending%20the%20ceremony%20scheduled%20for%20January%2022%2C%20why%20not%20also%20the%20Shakaracharya%20of%20Puri%2C%20who%20has%20also%20declined%20to%20be%20present%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlternately%2C%20why%20is%20the%20Sangh%20fighting%20shy%20of%20engaging%20the%20Shankaracharya%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EShastrartha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20or%20scholarly%20debate%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20hallowed%20traditions%20of%20the%20Sanatan%2C%20so%20that%20lay%20Hindus%20might%20better%20understand%20the%20intricacies%20of%20the%20issue%20at%20hand%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20now%2C%20it%20does%20seem%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20is%20closer%20to%20the%20Sanatan%20position%20than%20those%20who%20are%20so%20relentlessly%20propagating%20the%20Sanatan%20character%20of%20the%20event%20to%20come.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%2C%20would%20it%20not%20be%20apposite%20for%20media%20houses%20to%20foreground%20the%20historic%20nature%20of%20the%20schism%20here%20between%20the%20Shankaracharya%20and%20the%20forces%20of%20political%20Hinduism%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%2C%20which%20side%20may%20the%20nationalist%20corporates%20be%20on%20who%20now%20elbow%20the%20said%20media%20channels%20in%20establishment%20directions%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20it%20does%20seem%20to%20be%20the%20case%20that%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20has%20little%20reason%20to%20cower%2C%20given%20that%20its%20reservations%20have%20been%20so%20openly%20and%20authoritatively%20endorsed%20by%20the%20highest%20religious%20supremo%20among%20the%20Sanatan%20hierarchy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0It%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20the%20messaging%20wherewithal%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20has%20the%20resources%20to%20match%20the%20onslaught%20of%20the%20official%20armoury.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%2C%20thereby%20hangs%20an%20unlovely%20tale.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705066793000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11120348%2FPrime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_performing_Bhoomi_Pujan_at_%25E2%2580%2598Shree_Ram_Janmabhoomi_Mandir%25E2%2580%2599_in_Ayodhya_Uttar_Pradesh_on_August_05_2020.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fwho-represents-the-sanatan-the-seer-of-puri-or-shri-modi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Would%20it%20be%20apposite%20for%20media%20houses%20to%20foreground%20the%20historic%20nature%20of%20the%20schism%20between%20the%20Shankaracharya%20and%20the%20forces%20of%20political%20Hinduism%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fwho-represents-the-sanatan-the-seer-of-puri-or-shri-modi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Merry%20Christmas%3A%20Just%20Sriram%20Raghavan%20Showing%20off%20His%20Skills%20and%20Beguiling%20His%20Audience%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12184354%2FUntitled-design-13.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20was%20the%20last%20time%20a%20filmmaker%20went%20for%20a%20close-up%20on%20Katrina%20Kaif%E2%80%99s%20face%3F%20Kaif%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20actors%20working%20for%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20is%20not%20entirely%20known%20for%20her%20acting%20prowess.%20And%20yet%2C%20in%20Sriram%20Raghavan%E2%80%99s%20latest%20directorial%20venture%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMerry%20Christmas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20famous%20director%20closes%20in%20on%20that%20perfect%20face.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20does%20it%20say%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERaghavan%E2%80%99s%20brand%20of%20nothing-is-what-it-seems%20stories%20plant%20a%20doubt%20in%20the%20viewer%2C%20keeping%20us%20on%20our%20toes%2C%20forcing%20us%20to%20ask%20%E2%80%93%20what%20is%20Kaif%E2%80%99s%20face%20really%20conveying%3F%20Can%20we%20trust%20her%20affected%20delivery%2C%20when%20she%20talks%20about%20her%20drug-abuser%20husband%2C%20who%20is%20paranoid%20about%20her%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20only%20then%20that%20the%20essence%20of%20this%20unusual%20collaboration%20dawns%20on%20us%20%E2%80%93%20why%20Raghavan%20went%20with%20Kaif.%20It%E2%80%99s%20precisely%20because%20Kaif%E2%80%99s%20face%20is%20hard%20to%20read%20that%20it%20lends%20itself%20superbly%20to%20the%20cipher%20that%20her%20character%2C%20Maria%2C%20is.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FUUKdUNMgk7Q%3Fsi%3DQp0sHlempvPAV4E2%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20meet%20her%20at%20a%20busy%20Colaba%20restaurant%20with%20her%20daughter%2C%20Annie%2C%20where%20she%20has%20been%20stood%20up%20by%20a%20date.%20Maria%20aces%20the%20look%20of%C2%A0%20a%20hapless%2C%20young%20mother%20forced%20to%20spend%20Christmas%20eve%20by%20herself.%20Bumping%20into%20%E2%80%9CDubai-return%E2%80%9D%20Albert%20(Vijay%20Sethupathi)%20at%20the%20eatery%2C%20the%20mother-daughter%20meet%20him%20again%20inside%20a%20movie%20theatre%20at%20Regal%20showing%20%3Cem%3EPinocchio.%3C%2Fem%3E%20As%20a%20show%20of%20courtesy%2C%20Albert%20offers%20to%20drop%20them%20home%20%E2%80%93%20which%2C%20she%20assures%2C%20is%20a%20couple%20of%20lanes%20away.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20strangers%2C%20accompanied%20by%20a%20little%20girl%20and%20a%20giant%20teddy%20bear%2C%20make%20their%20way%20to%20Maria%E2%80%99s%20residence%20on%20Christmas%20eve.%20She%20offers%20him%20a%20drink%2C%20puts%20Annie%20to%20bed%2C%20and%20they%E2%80%99re%20soon%20exchanging%20their%20life%20stories.%20They%20discover%20how%20they%E2%80%99ve%20both%20loved%20and%20lost.%20She%20suggests%20they%20go%20out%20for%20a%20walk.%20An%20Arijit%20Singh%20ballad%20plays%20in%20the%20background.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20build-up%20for%20Sriram%20Raghavan%20is%20elaborate%2C%20and%20to%20his%20credit%2C%20not%20rushed.%20We%20know%20this%20is%20too%20good%20to%20be%20true%2C%20and%20Raghavan%20knows%20we%20know%20this.%20So%2C%20he%20deliberately%20makes%20us%20invest%20in%20this%20bizarre%20pairing%20%E2%80%93%20a%20diva%20from%20Hindi%20cinema%2C%20and%20the%20working-class%20hero%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20who%20has%20burst%20into%20superstardom%20only%20relatively%20recently.%20Their%20different%20dialects%2C%20backgrounds%2C%20acting%20energies%20%E2%80%93%20everything%20seems%20to%20contradict%20each%20other.%20Only%20until%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKaif%E2%80%99s%20laboured%20dialogue%20delivery%20unmasks%20the%20performance%20within%20the%20performance.%20Sethupathi%E2%80%99s%20loose%20body%20language%2C%20firms%20up%20when%20the%20time%20comes.%20The%20Richard%20Linklater%20rom-com%20version%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMerry%20Christmas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20where%20two%20strangers%20falling%20in%20love%20over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20night%2C%20makes%20way%20for%20the%20Sriram%20Raghavan%20noir%20we%20all%20came%20to%20see.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20corpse%20is%20discovered.%20People%20come%20clean%20about%20their%20past.%20The%20%E2%80%98love%20story%E2%80%99%20is%20derailed%2C%20but%20is%20it%20really%3F%20It%20would%20be%20unfair%20to%20reveal%20anything%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbout%20an%20hour%20into%20the%20141-minute%20film%2C%20is%20when%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMerry%20Christmas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20truly%20begins.%20Characters%20go%20their%20different%20ways%2C%20new%20characters%20bump%20into%20them%20and%20the%20entire%20premise%20comes%20together.%20In%20typical%20Raghavan%20fashion%2C%20the%20film%20starts%20with%20a%20split-screen%20shot%20of%20hands%20grinding%20tablets%2C%20and%20another%20set%20of%20hands%20making%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epodi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20masala%20and%20hiding%20a%20ring%20in%20it.%20As%20the%20film%20goes%20on%2C%20both%20scenes%20fill%20the%20necessary%20blanks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKaif%20is%20committed%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20and%20is%20serviceable%20for%20the%20film.%20It%E2%80%99s%20Sethupathi%2C%20who%20towers%20over%20the%20film%20with%20his%20easy%2C%20assured%20presence.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20left%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20unfinished%20in%20life%2C%20but%20never%20a%20bottle%20of%20chilled%20beer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks%20at%20one%20point.%20Raghavan%20laces%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20with%20a%20wild%20supporting%20cast%20including%20Sanjay%20Kapoor%2C%20Tinu%20Anand%2C%20Vinay%20Pathak%2C%20Ashwini%20Kalsekar%2C%20Pratima%20Kannan%20and%20Radhika%20Apte.%20It%E2%80%99s%20in%20the%20second%20hour%20that%20Raghavan%E2%80%99s%20filmmaking%20really%20gets%20down%20to%20business%2C%20staging%20weirdly%20comical%20scenes%2C%20which%20we%E2%80%99ve%20come%20to%20expect.%20No%20one%20is%20who%20they%20say%20they%20are%2C%20everyone%20is%20lying%20to%20some%20degree.%20In%20a%20situation%20like%20this%2C%20who%20do%20you%20really%20trust%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMerry%20Christmas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20nowhere%20as%20dense%20or%20convoluted%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAndhadhun%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2018)%2C%20but%20does%20that%20mean%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20step%20down%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20simple%2C%20relatively%20contained%20premise%20%E2%80%93%20one%20that%20bears%20all%20the%20dazzling%20technique%20of%20a%20Raghavan%20film.%20The%20detailing%20in%20the%20production%20design%20is%20fantastic%2C%20the%20music%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20Pritam%E2%80%99s%20ballads%20and%20a%20mix%20of%20Christmas%20hymns%2C%20Western%20orchestra%20and%20vintage%20Hindi%20film%20music%20(the%20film%20pays%20tribute%20to%20Shakti%20Samanta).%20Raghavan%20also%20makes%20sure%20to%20include%20his%20love%20for%20food%20and%20alcohol%2C%20with%20a%20scene%20featuring%20Albert%20making%20dosas%2C%20and%20multiple%20characters%20gulping%20their%20drinks%20in%20more%20than%20one%20scene.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20litmus%20test%20of%20Raghavan%E2%80%99s%20story%20lies%20in%20the%20final%20moments%2C%20when%20the%20audience%20becomes%20privy%20to%20the%20guilty%20party%2C%20and%20the%20thrill%20is%20will%20they%20get%20away%3F%20Raghavan%20drowns%20all%20the%20dialogue%20with%20a%20piece%20Western%20classical%20music%20as%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20final%20reveal%20takes%20place%2C%20and%20all%20hell%20breaks%20loose.%20This%20is%20someone%20at%20the%20height%20of%20his%20mastery%2C%20able%20to%20get%20to%20the%20essence%20of%20a%20scene%20best%20among%20his%20contemporaries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20might%20critique%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20initial%20staging%20portions%2C%20for%20how%20long%20Raghavan%20takes.%20If%20you%20ask%20me%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMerry%20Chritsmas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20feature-film%20sized%20flex%20by%20one%20of%20Hindi%20cinema%E2%80%99s%20most%20masterful%20filmmakers.%20We%E2%80%99re%20watching%20someone%20at%20his%20most%20assured.%20He%20takes%20his%20time%2C%20because%20he%20can.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705066221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12184354%2FUntitled-design-13.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmerry-christmas-sriram-raghavan-katrina-kaif-vijay-sethupathi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vijay%20Sethupathi%20shines%20in%20this%20suspense%20film.%20Katrina%20Kaif%20adds%20to%20the%20intrigue%20in%20a%20unique%20way.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmerry-christmas-sriram-raghavan-katrina-kaif-vijay-sethupathi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boeing%20faces%20additional%20safety%20scrutiny%20amid%20'other%20manufacturing%20problems'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705066200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F768x432%2Fskynews-boeing-f-alaska-airline_6415594.jpg%3F20240109063315%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fboeing-faces-additional-safety-scrutiny-amid-other-manufacturing-problems-13046841%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20flight%20safety%20regulators%20are%20to%20intensify%20their%20scrutiny%20of%20Boeing%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20mid-air%20panel%20blowout%20a%20week%20ago%20aboard%20