%20to%20cook%20gourmet%20food.%20There%2C%20she%20faces%20the%20dilemma%20of%20having%20to%20cook%20meat%20dishes.%20Her%20friend%2C%20a%20Muslim%20man%20(Farhan%2C%20played%20by%20Jai)%2C%20convinces%20her%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20necessarily%20wrong%20in%20cooking%20meat%20by%20citing%20a%20verse%20from%20Valmiki%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ERamayan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20Sanskrit%2C%20which%20features%20Ram%20and%20Lakshman%20hunting%20animals%20and%20cooking%20meat%20to%20assuage%20their%20hunger.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20exchange%20has%20Hindu%20zealots%20up%20in%20arms.%20Because%20some%20delicate%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20Hindu%20vegetarian%20sensibilities%20have%20been%20injured%20by%20the%20mere%20idea%20that%20Rama%20could%20be%20spoken%20of%20as%20eating%20meat%2C%20and%20that%20too%20at%20the%20time%20when%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Epranpratishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(life%20establishment)%20ritual%20around%20the%20idol%20of%20Ram%20in%20the%20new%20temple%20at%20Ayodhya%20is%20about%20to%20take%20place.%20Matters%20are%20further%20complicated%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20this%20occurs%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20film%20depicting%20a%20friendship%20between%20a%20Hindu%20woman%20and%20a%20Muslim%20man.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fayodhya-rss-bjp-vhp-ram-temple%5C%22%3EFour%20Decades%20of%20Milking%20a%20Deity%20in%20Ayodhya%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20not%20just%20the%20question%20of%20culinary%20blasphemy%2C%20but%20also%20the%20civilisational%20catastrophe%20of%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20is%20invoked.%20Police%20complaints%20against%20the%20filmmakers%20have%20been%20filed%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Maharashtra.%20And%20now%20Netflix%2C%20the%20OTT%20platform%20where%20the%20film%20was%20being%20screened%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fannapoorani-netfli