eshow%2F105218813.cms%5C%22%3Ein%20exchange%20for%20railways%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20alleges%20that%20Hema%20and%20Misa%20were%20also%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20illegal%20transactions%20in%20land%20and%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20course%2C%20Hridayanand%20Choudhary%2C%20a%20Grade%20C%20railways%20employee%20who%20served%20as%20an%20officer%20on%20special%20duty%20to%20Lalu%20when%20he%20was%20Union%20railways%20minister%20between%202004%20and%202009%2C%20figures%20in%20the%20chargesheet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20was%20the%20Grade%20C%20employee%20competent%20enough%20to%20get%20the%20railway%20minister%20to%20carry%20out%20transactions%20for%20Grade%20D%20jobs%20in%20exchange%20for%20land%20without%20the%20involvement%20of%20any%20top%20railways%20functionaries%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20moot%20question.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20its%20supporters%20have%20consistently%20used%20the%20Rs%20950%20crore%20fodder%20scam%20to%20stoke%20Lalu%E2%80%99s%20perception%20as%20a%20corrupt%20leader.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20fundamental%20difference%20between%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20Union%20investigating%20agencies%20have%20approached%20the%20%E2%80%98land-for-jobs%E2%80%99%20scam%20and%20the%20fodder%20scam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20228px)%2085vw%2C%20228px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12160848%2FLPY-228x300.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22228%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12160848%2FLPY-228x300.jpeg%20228w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12160848%2FLPY.jpeg%20639w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-692682%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ELalu%20is%20one%20of%20the%20highest-profile%20politicians%20to%20be%20convicted%20in%20the%20fodder%20scam.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40laluprasadrjd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20many%20as%20five%20senior%20IAS%20officers%3B%20over%2075%20employees%20of%20the%20Bihar%20animal%20husbandry%20department%3B%20several%20producers%20and%20suppliers%20of%20the%20cattle%E2%80%99s%20feed%2C%20fodder%20and%20medicines%3B%20and%20top%20politicians%20across%20party%20lines%2C%20including%20the%20BJP%20and%20two%20former%20chief%20ministers%20(Jagannath%20Mishra%20and%20Lalu)%20figured%20in%20the%20fodder%20scam%20cases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20cases%20pertained%20to%20the%20withdrawals%20from%20the%20treasuries%20worth%20Rs%20950%20crore%20in%20excess%20of%20budgetary%20allocations%20for%20the%20animal%20husbandry%20department%20over%20a%20span%20of%20sixteen%20years%20(1980-1996)%2C%20as%20pointed%20out%20in%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%E2%80%99s%20reports%20then.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReacting%20to%20the%20ED%20naming%20Lalu%E2%80%99s%20daughters%20in%20its%20chargesheet%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20spokesperson%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Manoj%20Jha%20said%20to%20the%20media%20in%20Delhi%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ED%20is%20doing%20this%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20two%20persons%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20power%20structure%20to%20trouble%20their%20political%20opponents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20fictitious%20case%20in%20which%20several%20FIRs%20were%20filed%20in%202008%2C%20and%20the%20CBI%20and%20the%20ED%20closed%20them%20in%202011%20after%20finding%20no%20evidence.%20The%20investigating%20agencies%20reopened%20it%20suddenly%20in%202021-22%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Operation%20Lotus%E2%80%99%20that%20worked%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20boomeranged%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20chargesheet%20in%20a%20special%20PMLA%20court%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20January%209%20is%20a%20clear-cut%20example%20of%20political%20vendetta.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJha%20cited%20how%20the%20leaders%20of%20Delhi%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Kerala%20%E2%80%93%20all%20non-BJP%20ruled%20states%20%E2%80%93%20were%20being%20targeted%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20the%20CBI.%20He%20apprehended%20that%20the%20investigating%20agencies%20may%20heap%20more%20trumped-up%20charges%20on%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20rivals%20ahead%20of%20January%2022%2C%20the%20date%20of%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMedia%20focus%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20mainstream%20media%20%E2%80%93%20print%20and%20electronic%20%E2%80%93%20largely%20downplayed%20or%20ignored%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20statements.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20ED%20and%20CBI%20are%20issuing%20what%20Jha%20described%20as%20%E2%80%9Csummons%20after%20summons%E2%80%9D%20to%20opponents%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20party%20like%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20cadres%20of%20the%20RSS%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20moving%20door-to-door%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eakshat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20collect%20contributions%20from%20people%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20and%20Hindi%20newspapers%20from%20Patna%20to%20Lucknow%20and%20Delhi%20were%20full%20of%20stories%20on%20Ram%2C%20Sita%2C%20Ayodhya%2C%20Varanasi%20and%20Mathura.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIntentionally%20or%20otherwise%2C%20the%20visuals%20and%20narratives%20in%20the%20mass%20media%20are%20largely%20creating%20the%20perception%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20resurrected%20Lord%20Ram%20from%20the%20shackles%20of%20medieval%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eghulami%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(slavery)%20and%20restored%20him%20in%20th