r-hesitant-in-going-to-ayodhya-dham-sushil-modi-question-9169869.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESenior%20BJP%20leader%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%20has%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20invited%20everyone%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epran%20pratishtha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Bconsecration%5D%20ceremony%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20as%20such%2C%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20who%20offer%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echadar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emazar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20and%20bow%20down%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egurdwara%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Es%2C%20must%20attend%20the%20January%2022%20event.%20There%20should%20be%20no%20politics%20on%20such%20a%20divine%20occasion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20Hindutva%20cadres%20and%20supporters%20are%20heard%20discussing%20mirthfully%20how%20Nitish%2C%20Lalu%20as%20well%20as%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20%E2%80%93%20Samajwadi%20Party%20president%20and%20chief%20minister%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%93%20were%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98fix%E2%80%99%20over%20the%20issue%20and%20how%20they%20would%20likely%20suffer%20politically%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20RSS%20and%20BJP%20blowing%20up%20religious%20issues%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bihar%20media%20is%20largely%20agog%20with%20speculation%20about%20how%20Lalu%20was%20%E2%80%98pressuring%E2%80%99%20Nitish%20to%20make%20his%20son%20Tejashwi%20the%20CM%3B%20how%20Nitish%20is%20upset%20at%20not%20being%20nominated%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98convener%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%3B%20and%20how%20Nitish%20has%20been%20working%20on%20going%20back%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-parties-after-the-defeat-preparing-for-2024%5C%22%3EForging%20Genuine%20Solidarity%20With%20Each%20Other%20Is%20the%20Way%20Forward%20for%20the%20INDIA%20Alliance%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20stories%20have%20been%20doing%20the%20rounds%20ever%20since%20the%20Bihar%20CM%20dumped%20the%20BJP%20in%20August%202022%20and%20joined%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20with%20the%20RJD%2C%20Congress%20and%20Left%20parties%2C%20despite%20leaders%20from%20his%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20and%20the%20RJD%20unequivocally%20denying%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20process%2C%20the%20news%20of%20over%204.5%20lakh%20youths%20getting%20jobs%3B%2065%25%20reservation%20for%20OBCs%2C%20SCs%2C%20STs%20and%20the%20extremely%20backward%20classes%3B%20as%20well%20as%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20work%20on%20education%2C%20health%20and%20infrastructure%20has%20been%20relegated%20to%20the%20periphery.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20that%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20(who%20are%20now%20also%20known%20as%20leaders%20of%20INDIA)%20are%20not%20unnerved%20by%20the%20developments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COf%20course%2C%20we%20are%20anxious.%20The%20BJP%20under%20the%20cover%20of%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20has%20let%20loose%20the%20investigating%20agencies%20to%20trouble%20Lalu%2C%20Tejashwi%20and%20others%20who%20are%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20saffron%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jha%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20will%20not%20be%20cowed%20down.%20We%20will%20take%20the%20battle%20to%20the%20court%20of%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fnalin-verma%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENalin%20Verma%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%2C%20and%20independent%20